the longitudinal photon discussed in eq. (1). A simple prescription to
systematically solve eqs. (2) and (3) for an infinite number of zero-norm
states was given recently in Ref[7]. A more thorough understanding of the
solution of these equations and their relation to space-time 
 symmetry of toy D=2 string was discussed in Ref[9].  

