scattering amplitudes of two different string states at the second massive
level. This proportionality constant is, as suggested by Gross,
independent of the scattering angle  and the order (or G)
of string perturbation theory. Most importantly, we now understand
that it is originated from D zero-norm state in the OCFQ
spectrum of the string! 

